videos.description: Greg Stroman takes it 61-yards to the house for Virginia Tech's first touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Stroman's punt return for a TD puts Virginia Tech on the board

videos.description: Josh Jackson throws a 39-yard pass to Sean Savoy to put Virginia Tech in the red zone.
videos.headline: Savoy makes acrobatic catch

videos.description: Josh Jackson finds Travon McMillian for a four-yard touchdown to give Virginia Tech a 17-0 lead.
videos.headline: McMillian's TD increases Virginia Tech's lead

videos.description: Terrell Edmunds intercepts Joe Walker's pass.
videos.headline: Walker's pass tipped, intercepted by Edmunds

videos.description: Malcolm Brown forces fumble to give Delaware the ball back.
videos.headline: Delaware regains possession after forced fumble

videos.description: Josh Jackson throws a 28-yard touchdown pass to Cam Phillips in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Defender falls as Phillips makes TD grab

videos.description: Tremaine Edmunds sacks Joe Walker for a 14-yard loss and forces a turnover.
videos.headline: Edmunds sacks Walker, forces turnover

videos.description: Forrest Conoly says he was surprised Virginia Tech couldn't establish a running game, says Hokies will have to continue to work on running game.
videos.headline: Conoly breaks down Virginia Tech's shutout win against Delaware
